<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Код подтверждения</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fdf6e4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 450px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 5px solid #ff9800;
            animation: slideUp 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                transform: translateY(50px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .code-container {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff9800;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            user-select: all;
            -webkit-user-select: all;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        a {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #e68a00;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        a:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Ваш код подтверждения</h1>
    <div class="code-container">{{authCode}}</div>
    <p>Если вы не запрашивали код подтверждения, просто проигнорируйте это письмо.</p>
    <div class="footer">© ВопроСФУ, {{currentYear}}</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
